<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>EUV - Sala de Espera</title>

  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png"/>

  <link href="/addons/2048/style/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1 class="titulo">Aguarde os outros jogadores concluírem seus desafios!</h1>
  <h2 class="titulo-h2">Você pode <i>ajudar seus amigos</i> enquanto aguarda ou aprimorar sua matemática com o jogo abaixo..</h2>
  <hr>  
  <div class="container">    
    <div class="heading">
      <h1 class="title">2048</h1>
      <div class="scores-container">
        <div class="score-container">0</div>
        <div class="best-container">0</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="above-game">
      <p class="game-intro">Junte os números e consiga o bloco com<strong> 2048!</strong></p>
      <a class="restart-button">Novo jogo</a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-container">
      <div class="game-message">
        <p></p>
        <div class="lower">
	        <a class="keep-playing-button">Continue</a>
          <a class="retry-button">Tente novamente</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-container">
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tile-container">

      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="game-explanation">
      <strong class="important">Como jogar:</strong> Use suas <strong>teclas de seta</strong> para mover os blocos. Quando dois blocos com o mesmo número se tocam, eles <strong> se transformam em um!</strong>
    </p>
    <hr>
    <p>
    Created by <a href="http://gabrielecirulli.com" target="_blank">Gabriele Cirulli.</a> Based on <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/1024!/id823499224" target="_blank">1024 by Veewo Studio</a> and conceptually similar to <a href="http://asherv.com/threes/" target="_blank">Threes by Asher Vollmer.</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <script src="/addons/2048/js/bind_polyfill.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/classlist_polyfill.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/animframe_polyfill.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/keyboard_input_manager.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/html_actuator.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/grid.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/tile.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/local_storage_manager.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/game_manager.js"></script>
  <script src="/addons/2048/js/application.js"></script>
  <!-- socket libraries -->
  <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/player/waitingRoom.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
